makewiz
=======

Syntax: makewiz <player>

Promotes an online mortal to Apprentice wizard and applies the Godling
RCC. The player must be online.

Apprentices are temporary staff:
  - position: apprentice
  - who tag: [Apprentice]
  - workroom created under /realms/<name>/
  - no role staff tools yet

Full staff roles still use setrole after apprenticeship tasks:

  makewiz ptdacon
  (tasks...)
  setrole ptdacon domain

Restricted to admin-level wizards. Logged to /log/adm/makewiz.

See also: help setrole, help staff *wizard staff
